6:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"Gravatar: Profile Pages <3 hCard\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"http://blog.gravatar.com/?p=218\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"http://blog.gravatar.com/2010/06/22/hcard-profile-pages/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2805:\"<p>Did you know that your profile pages are fully marked up using <a href=\"http://microformats.org/wiki/hcard\">hCard</a>? hCard is a <a href=\"http://microformats.org/\">microformat</a> for programmatically embedding information about people, companies, organizations, and places in HTML and other markup languages. The screenshot below describes some of the main markup involved on a profile page</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Email address</strong> marked up with <code>class=email</code> (only available via JS/client-side parsing due to spam-protection measures)</li>\n<li><strong>IM accounts</strong> marked up using <code>class=url</code> (some values only available via JS/client-side parsing due to spam-protection measures)</li>\n<li><strong>Phone numbers</strong> marked up with <code>class=tel</code> (using type/value subproperties)</li>\n<li><strong>Verified accounts</strong> marked up with <code>class=url</code> and <code>rel=me</code></li>\n<li><strong>Name</strong> marked up with <code>class=fn</code></li>\n<li><strong>Personal Links</strong> are marked up with <code>class=url</code></li>\n<li><strong>Image</strong> (main Gravatar) is marked up using <code>class=photo</code></li>\n</ol>\n<div id=\"attachment_219\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://gravatar.files.wordpress.com/2010/06/hcard-details.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-219\" title=\"hcard-details\" src=\"http://gravatar.files.wordpress.com/2010/06/hcard-details.png?w=700&#038;h=524\" alt=\"hCard on Profile Pages\" width=\"700\" height=\"524\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">hCard on Profile Pages</p></div>\n<p>There&#8217;s more profile-data goodness coming soon, so check back here for the latest.</p>\n<br />  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godigg/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/digg/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/goreddit/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/reddit/gravatar.wordpress.com/218/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=blog.gravatar.com&blog=1886259&post=218&subd=gravatar&ref=&feed=1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 22 Jun 2010 20:26:41 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b: