INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2010-06-23 18:19:59','2010-06-23 18:19:59','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','trash','open','open','','hello-world','','','2010-06-29 09:05:33','2010-06-29 14:05:33','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2010-06-23 18:19:59','2010-06-23 18:19:59','There are other wrestling camps out there.  The difference is, the  Intensive Camp is more than simply a wrestling camp. I promise if you do  what\'s required, this experience will change your life. I guarantee it.\r\n\r\nI look at it from the perspective of the young, developing wrestler.  You know you can succeed if you focus and work hard, but there is a  limit to how hard a coach can push during the regular season (weight  cutting, school, competition, etc.).\r\n\r\nWhat you need to break through all the barriers is an experience that  gives you three important things:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Focus.</strong> J Rob Intensive Camps eliminate all  distractions for 10, 14 or 28 days. No family. No school. No social  outings. This extreme immersion changes how you view your limitations.  You surrender yourself to a highly concentrated and very structured  environment that requires you each and every day to consistently do  more.  Youre stretched to your limits daily. And as a result, you  realize that youre capable of so much more than YOU ever thought  possible.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Mental Strength.</strong> A lot of coaches and athletes  think that attending a J Rob camp is only about getting in great shape  and gaining technical knowledge and skills. Nothing could be farther  from the truth. I constantly hear people remark, You go to camp and get  in great shape, but you cant use it for 5 months. Camp isnt just  about physical training; its about extending your boundaries  mentallywhich is the real key to success.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Lasting Impact.</strong> The more intense an experience, the  more you learn and the longer you will retain it. When a camper leaves  my camp, they bring something home with them that allows them to be not  just better wrestlers, but better leaders, students, sons, daughters and  citizens. J Rob camps instill new skills in multiple areas of life.  Camp is about developing wrestling and life skills, and that requires  time, attitude, effort andabove allintensity.</li>\r\n</ol>','Why J Rob?','','publish','closed','closed','','whyjrob','','','2010-06-30 10:07:35','2010-06-30 15:07:35','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(3,1,'2010-06-23 18:20:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2010-06-23 18:20:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?p=3',0,'post','',0),(4,1,'2010-06-25 13:32:05','2010-06-25 13:32:05','<!-- flash-area -->\r\n<div id=\"placeholder-1\" class=\"flash-area\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"images/flash.jpg\" alt=\"flash01\" width=\"848\" height=\"269\" />\r\n\r\n</div>','Homepage','','publish','closed','closed','','homepage','','','2010-06-28 10:27:18','2010-06-28 15:27:18','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?page_id=4',0,'page','',0),(5,1,'2010-06-25 13:31:46','2010-06-25 13:31:46','','Homepage','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision','','','2010-06-25 13:31:46','2010-06-25 13:31:46','',4,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?p=5',0,'revision','',0),(6,1,'2010-06-25 10:25:49','2010-06-25 15:25:49','<img title=\"camp-overview\" src=\"http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/camp-overview.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"133\" align=\"left\" />J Robinson Intensive Camps offers 28, 14, and 10-Day Intensive  Wrestling Camps designed to refine a young wrestlers technical skill  and physical conditioning as well as provide them with the life skills  they need to define and reach their highest goals.\r\n\r\nWe also have 5-Day Technique and Takedown Camps aimed at honing a  young wrestlers fundamental skill.\r\n\r\nFor more information on our camps, please click on a topic to the  side.','Camp Details','','publish','closed','closed','','camp-details','','','2010-06-30 09:52:05','2010-06-30 14:52:05','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?page_id=6',0,'page','',0),(7,1,'2010-06-25 10:25:34','2010-06-25 15:25:34','','News','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision','','','2010-06-25 10:25:34','2010-06-25 15:25:34','',6,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?p=7',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2010-06-25 13:32:05','2010-06-25 13:32:05','','Homepage','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-2','','','2010-06-25 13:32:05','2010-06-25 13:32:05','',4,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/8',0,'revision','',0),(9,1,'2010-06-25 10:31:16','2010-06-25 15:31:16','','Homepage','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-3','','','2010-06-25 10:31:16','2010-06-25 15:31:16','',4,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/9',0,'revision','',0),(14,1,'2010-06-23 18:19:59','2010-06-23 18:19:59','This is an example of a WordPress page, you could edit this to put information about yourself or your site so readers know where you are coming from. You can create as many pages like this one or sub-pages as you like and manage all of your content inside of WordPress.','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision','','','2010-06-23 18:19:59','2010-06-23 18:19:59','',2,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/14',0,'revision','',0),(10,1,'2010-06-28 08:38:32','2010-06-28 13:38:32','<!-- flash-area -->\n<div id=\"placeholder-1\" class=\"flash-area\">\n\n<img src=\"images/flash.jpg\" alt=\"flash01\" width=\"848\" height=\"269\" />\n\n</div>\n<!-- video-area -->\n<div class=\"video-area\">\n<div class=\"video-box\">\n<h2 class=\"txt-new-blood\"><a class=\"btn-play\" title=\"New Blood\" rel=\"lightbox\" href=\"video/new-blood.swf\">New Blood</a></h2>\n<div class=\"video-holder\">\n<div class=\"holder\"><img src=\"images/title.png\" alt=\"image01\" />\n<a class=\"btn-play\" title=\"New Blood\" rel=\"lightbox