 and skills. Nothing could be farther  from the truth. I constantly hear people remark, You go to camp and get  in great shape, but you cant use it for 5 months. Camp isnt just  about physical training; its about extending your boundaries  mentallywhich is the real key to success.\r\n	Lasting Impact. The more intense an experience, the  more you learn and the longer you will retain it. When a camper leaves  my camp, they bring something home with them that allows them to be not  just better wrestlers, but better leaders, students, sons, daughters and  citizens. J Rob camps instill new skills in multiple areas of life.  Camp is about developing wrestling and life skills, and that requires  time, attitude, effort andabove allintensity.\r\n','','','publish','open','open','','16','','','2010-06-30 10:15:33','2010-06-30 15:15:33','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?p=16',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(17,1,'2010-06-28 15:33:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2010-06-28 15:33:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?p=17',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(18,1,'2010-06-28 15:43:24','2010-06-28 20:43:24','','camp-overview','','inherit','open','open','','camp-overview','','','2010-06-28 15:43:24','2010-06-28 20:43:24','',6,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/camp-overview.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(19,1,'2010-06-29 15:59:14','2010-06-29 20:59:14','<a href=\"http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/camp-overview.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-18\" title=\"camp-overview\" src=\"http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/camp-overview.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"133\" /></a>J Robinson Intensive Camps offers 28, 14, and 10-Day Intensive  Wrestling Camps designed to refine a young wrestlers technical skill  and physical conditioning as well as provide them with the life skills  they need to define and reach their highest goals.\n\nWe also have