i>2X World Team Member</li>\r\n	<li>Pan American Coach</li>\r\n	<li>4X Assistant Olympic Coach</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nCoach Robinson will be at every camp. J resides at the Intensive Camps every summer and is very accessible to campers and parents. At the beginning and end of the Intensive Camps, J will host an informational session for parents to help them better understand their son/daughters camp experience. Details regarding these information sessions will be in the confirmation packet.\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" width=\"628\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>JOE RUSSELL</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img11.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul class=\"staff-list\">\r\n	<li>Assistant Coach - University of Minnesota</li>\r\n	<li>Head Coach - MN Storm Junior and University World Teams</li>\r\n	<li>4X Coach of FILA Junior Freestyle &amp; Greco-Roman National Championship Teams</li>\r\n	<li>2X Junior National Champion</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td width=\"306\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>BRANDON EGGUM</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img12.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul class=\"staff-list\">\r\n	<li>Assistant Coach - University of Minnesota</li>\r\n	<li>2001 World Silver Medalist</li>\r\n	<li>2002 Pan American Freestyle Runner-up</li>\r\n	<li>2X Big Ten Champion</li>\r\n	<li>3X NCAA All-American</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>LUKE BECKER</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img13.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul class=\"staff-list\">\r\n	<li>Assistant Coach - University of Minnesota</li>\r\n	<li>NCAA Division I Champion</li>\r\n	<li>4X NCAA Division I All-American</li>\r\n	<li>2X Big 10 Champion</li>\r\n	<li>3X MN State Champion</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td valign=\