y basis.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>SAMPLE DAILY SCHEDULE</h4>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/tshirt.png\" alt=\"J Robinson Intensive Wrestling Camps\" /></div>\r\n<table width=\"277\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\">6:30</td>\r\n<td width=\"230\">Wake-Up</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>6:45</td>\r\n<td>Running and/or Weight Training</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7:30</td>\r\n<td>Breakfast</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>10:15</td>\r\n<td>Technique Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>12:00</td>\r\n<td>Lunch</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>3:00</td>\r\n<td>Hard Wrestling Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>5:00</td>\r\n<td>Dinner</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7:30</td>\r\n<td>Motivation/Mental Attitude</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>8:00</td>\r\n<td>Running and/or Weight Training</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11:00</td>\r\n<td>Lights Out</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<hr />Coach Robinson will be at every camp. J resides at the Intensive Camps every summer and is very accessible to campers and parents. At the beginning and end of the Intensive Camps, J will host an informational session for parents to help them better understand their son/daughters camp experience. Details regarding these information sessions will be in the confirmation packet.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Intensive Camps','','publish','closed','closed','','intensive-camps','','','2010-06-30 12:06:33','2010-06-30 17:06:33','',6,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net',0,'page','',0),(128,1,'2010-06-29 10:07:48','2010-06-29 15:07:48','','tshirt','','inherit','open','open','','tshirt','','','2010-06-29 10:07:48','2010-06-29 15:07:48','',127,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/tshirt.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(129,1,'2010-06-29 10:08:15','2010-06-29 15:08:15','<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"item\">\n<div class=\"tertnav\">\n\n<a href=\"intensive_dates.php\">Dates/Locations</a> | <a href=\"intensive_discounts.php\">Di