r\n\r\n','','','publish','open','open','','144','','','2010-06-29 10:12:42','2010-06-29 15:12:42','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?p=144',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(145,1,'2010-06-29 10:12:42','2010-06-29 15:12:42','\r\n\r\n\r\nDates/Locations | Discounts/Pricing | Facilities/Housing | Travel Arrangements | Insurance/Key Deposit\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nINTENSIVE CAMP OVERVIEW\r\n\r\n\r\nAre you ready for the challenge of a lifetime? Since 1978, J Robinson and his staff have provided an unparalleled training experience for thousands of wrestlers across the nation each summer.\r\n\r\nIn teaching a deeper understanding of the skills of discipline, sacrifice, dedication, hard work, responsibility, and accountability, you will be pushed to the limits physically and mentally, resulting in a dramatic change in the way you approach wrestling as well as life.\r\n\r\nWe are committed to training you in a way no other program can by increasing performance levels and giving you a new appreciation for what hard work really means.\r\n\r\nThe undisputed leader in intensive camp, J Robinson features a skilled staff of current and former collegiate wrestlers, top coaches and cliniciansall hosted at top-notch athletic facilities.\r\n\r\nIf not now, when? Take the J Robinson Intensive Camp challenge  GET INTENSE!\r\n\r\nThe Intensive Camp is designed for wrestlers 14-18 years of age. The multi-faceted training model emphasizes a high-energy conditioning routine designed to test athletes physically and mentally on a daily basis.\r\n\r\n\r\nSAMPLE DAILY SCHEDULE\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n6:30\r\nWake-Up\r\n\r\n\r\n6:45\r\nRunning and/or Weight Training\r\n\r\n\r\n7:30\r\nBreakfast\r\n\r\n\r\n10:15\r\nTechnique Practice\r\n\r\n\r\n12:00\r\nLunch\r\n\r\n\r\n3:00\r\nHard Wrestling Practice\r\n\r\n\r\n5:00\r\nDinner\r\n\r\n\r\n7:30\r\nMotivation/Mental Attitude\r\n\r\n\r\n8:00\r\nRunning and/or Weight Training\r\n\r\n\r\n11:00\r\nLights Out\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCoach Robinson will be at every camp. J resi