/uploads/2010/06/pa2.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\nLock Haven University, Lock Haven, PA\r\n\r\nJuly 5-9, 2010\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<h2>MINNESOTA</h2>\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/mn.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\nUniversity of Minnesota, Minneapolis, MN\r\n\r\nJuly 11-15, 2010\r\n\r\n<strong>YOUTH: </strong>July 11-15, 2010\r\n\r\nJuly 18-22, 2010\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<h2>CALIFORNIA</h2>\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/az.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\nAzusa Pacific University, Azusa, CA\r\n\r\nJuly 18-22, 2010\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<h2>WASHINGTON</h2>\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/wa.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /><a href=\"http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/mn.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-84\" title=\"mn\" src=\"http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/mn.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"72\" /></a></div>\r\nCentral Washington University, Ellensburg, WA\r\n\r\nAugust 1-5, 2010\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Facilities','','inherit','open','open','','66-revision-4','','','2010-06-29 14:52:19','2010-06-29 19:52:19','',66,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/160',0,'revision','',0),(161,1,'2010-06-29 10:10:05','2010-06-29 15:10:05','<div class=\"text\">\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"tertnav\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"intensive_dates.php\">Dates/Locations</a> | <a href=\"intensive_discounts.php\">Discounts/Pricing</a> | <a href=\"intensive_facilities.php\">Facilities/Housing</a> | <a href=\"intensive_travel.php\">Travel Arrangements</a> | <a href=\"intensive_insurance.php\">Insurance/Key Deposit</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>INTENSIVE CAMP OVERVIEW</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n\r\nAre you ready for the challenge of a lifetime? Since 1978, J Robinson and his staff have provided an unparalleled training experience for thousands of wrestlers across the nation each summer.\r\n\r\nIn teaching a deeper understanding of the skills of discipline, sacrifice, dedication, hard work, responsibility, and accountability, you will be pushed to the limits physically and mentally, resulting in a dramatic change in the way you approach wrestling as well as life.\r\n\r\nWe are committed to training you in a way no other program can by increasing performance levels and giving you a new appreciation for what hard work really means.\r\n\r\nThe undisputed leader in intensive camp, J Robinson features a skilled staff of current and former collegiate wrestlers, top coaches and cliniciansall hosted at top-notch athletic facilities.\r\n\r\nIf not now, when? Take the J Robinson Intensive Camp challenge  GET INTENSE!\r\n\r\n<hr />The Intensive Camp is designed for wrestlers 14-18 years of age. The multi-faceted training model emphasizes a high-energy conditioning routine designed to test athletes physically and mentally on a daily basis.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>SAMPLE DAILY SCHEDULE</h4>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/tshirt.png\" alt=\"J Robinson Intensive Wrestling Camps\" /></div>\r\n<table width=\"277\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\">6:30</td>\r\n<td width=\"230\">Wake-Up</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>6:45</td>\r\n<td>Running and/or Weight Training</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7:30</td>\r\n<td>Breakfast</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>10:15</td>\r\n<td>Technique Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>12:00</td>\r\n<td>Lunch</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>3:00</td>\r\n<td>Hard Wrestling Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>5:00</td>\r\n<td>Dinner</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7:30</td>\r\n<td>Motivation/Mental Attitude</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>8:00</td>\r\n<td>Running and/or Weight Training</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11:00</td>\r\n<td>Lights Out</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<hr />Coach Robinson will be at every camp. J resides at the Intensive Camps every summer and is very accessible to campers and parents. At the beginning and end of the Intensive Camps, J will host an informational session for parents to help them better understand their son/daughters camp experience. Details regarding these information sessions will be in the confirmation packet.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Intensive Camps','','inherit','open','open','','127-revision-3','','','2010-06-29 10:10:05','2010-06-29 15:10:05','',127,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/161',0,'revision','',0),(269,1,'2010-06-30 12:00:27','2010-06-30 17:00:27','<div class=\"text\">\r\n<h3>TRAVEL ARRANGEMENTS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jrob/images/takedown-travel.jpg\" alt=\"Travel Arrangements\" /></div>\r\nTravel arrangements to and from camp are the responsibility of each camper.\r\n\r\nCampers are to arrive the first day of camp and leave the last day of camp. Check in is from 12:00-2:00 pm on the first day of camp; check out is from 12:00-1:00 pm on the last day of camp. Travel arrangements to and from camp are the responsibility of each individual camper.\r\n\r\nJ Robinson Camps has a relationship with Teel\'s Travel for preferred airfare pricing. Contact Darcie by phone (800-233-3225), email (<a href=\"mailto:Darcie@Travel-Planners.com\">Darcie@Travel-Planners.com</a>) or online at <a href=\"http://www.travel-planners.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Travel-Planners.com</a>.\r\n\r\nRound-trip transportation to and from the airport is provided by the camps for $25 per camper. Please check your confirmation materials for the correct airport for your camp.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Travel Arrangements','','inherit','open','open','','252-revision-2','','','2010-06-30 12:00:27','2010-06-30 17:00:27','',252,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/269',0,'revision','',0),(162,1,'2010-06-30 07:28:58','2010-06-30 12:28:58','<div class=\"text\">\r\n\r\nJ Robinson Wrestling Camps are directed by NCAA Division I Champion coaches along with Olympic Medalist and All-American wrestlers. Active University of Minnesota wrestlers serve as supporting staff at most camps while our technique training programs across the country feature regional all-star talent. Our premier roster of coaches and wrestlers will train side-by-side with campers and exemplify the dedication, discipline and work ethic that are the core values of J Robinson Camps.\r\n<h3>J ROBINSON</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img10.gif\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Head Coach University of Minnesota</li>\r\n	<li>3X NCAA Division I Championships (2001, 2002 and 2007)</li>\r\n	<li>2001 NCAA Division I Coach of the Year</li>\r\n	<li>1998 NCAA Division I Co-Coach of the Year</li>\r\n	<li>4X Big Ten Coach of the Year</li>\r\n	<li>1972 Olympic Team Member</li>\r\n	<li>2X World Team Member</li>\r\n	<li>Pan American Coach</li>\r\n	<li>4X Assistant Olympic Coach</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\nCoach Robinson will be at every camp. J resides at the Intensive Camps every summer and is very accessible to campers and parents. At the beginning and end of the Intensive Camps, J will host an informational session for parents to help them better understand their son/daughters camp experience. Details regarding these information sessions will be in the confirmation packet.\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" width=\"628\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>JOE RUSSELL</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img11.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul class=\"staff-list\">\r\n	<li>Assistant Coach - University of Minnesota</li>\r\n	<li>Head Coach - MN Storm Junior and University World Teams</li>\r\n	<li>4X Coach of FILA Junior Freestyle &amp; Greco-Roman National Championship Teams</li>\r\n	<li>2X Junior National Champion</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td width=\"306\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>BRANDON EGGUM</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img12.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul class=\"staff-list\">\r\n	<li>Assistant Coach - University of Minnesota</li>\r\n	<li>2001 World Silver Medalist</li>\r\n	<li>2002 Pan American Freestyle Runner-up</li>\r\n	<li>2X Big Ten Champion</li>\r\n	<li>3X NCAA All-American</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>LUKE BECKER</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img13.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul class=\"staff-list\">\r\n	<li>Assistant Coach - University of Minnesota</li>\r\n	<li>NCAA Division I Champion</li>\r\n	<li>4X NCAA Division I All-American</li>\r\n	<li>2X Big 10 Champion</li>\r\n	<li>3X MN State Champion</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>CURT FOLEY</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img14.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul class=\"staff-list\">\r\n	<li>Director of Wrestling Operations J Robinson Wrestling Camps</li>\r\n	<li>Head Wrestling Coach Dakota County Technical College</li>\r\n	<li>Assistant Coach/Head Recruiting Coordinator Minnesota State University-Moorhead</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>MIKE McGIVERN</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/img15.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\n<ul class=\"staff-list\">\r\n	<li>NCAA All-American University of Iowa</li>\r\n	<li>Member of 3 NCAA Championship Teams</li>\r\n	<li>2X Big Ten Runner-up</li>\r\n	<li>J Robinson Intensive Camp Staff Member Since 1979</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>COUNSELORS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n\r\n2010 Counselors Coming Soon!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Staff','','inherit'