el emphasizes a high-energy conditioning routine designed to test athletes physically and mentally on a daily basis.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>SAMPLE DAILY SCHEDULE</h4>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/tshirt.png\" alt=\"J Robinson Intensive Wrestling Camps\" /></div>\r\n<table width=\"277\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\">6:30</td>\r\n<td width=\"230\">Wake-Up</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>6:45</td>\r\n<td>Running and/or Weight Training</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7:30</td>\r\n<td>Breakfast</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>10:15</td>\r\n<td>Technique Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>12:00</td>\r\n<td>Lunch</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>3:00</td>\r\n<td>Hard Wrestling Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>5:00</td>\r\n<td>Dinner</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7:30</td>\r\n<td>Motivation/Mental Attitude</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>8:00</td>\r\n<td>Running and/or Weight Training</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11:00</td>\r\n<td>Lights Out</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<hr />Coach Robinson will be at every camp. J resides at the Intensive Camps every summer and is very accessible to campers and parents. At the beginning and end of the Intensive Camps, J will host an informational session for parents to help them better understand their son/daughters camp experience. Details regarding these information sessions will be in the confirmation packet.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Intensive Camps','','inherit','open','open','','127-revision-5','','','2010-06-30 10:04:28','2010-06-30 15:04:28','',127,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/268',0,'revision','',0),(165,1,'2010-06-30 09:14:21','2010-06-30 14:14:21','CAMP FEES INCLUDE:\r\n\r\nTRAINING\r\n\r\n	Live wrestling and hard drilling with new techniques introduced each day\r\n	Daily conditioning (includes group runs, weight training and cross-training)\r\n	A 3-step review of all new techniques led by J Rob staff in a small group format\r\n	Training with w