cian is required.</p>\n\n\n						  </div>\n                        <h4>KEY DEPOSITS</h4>\n                          <div class=\"item\">\n                            <p>A $60 key/damage room deposit is required for all resident campers. This is in excess to your camp fees. The $60 will be returned (in cash) when the camper has cleared the check out procedure and their room is cleared.</p>\n                            \n                      </div></div>','Insurance/Key Deposit','','inherit','open','open','','244-revision','','','2010-06-30 11:55:58','2010-06-30 16:55:58','',244,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/245',0,'revision','',0),(250,1,'2010-06-30 11:59:39','2010-06-30 16:59:39','<div class=\"text\">\r\n<div class=\"columns\">\r\n<div class=\"col\">\r\n<h1><em>FACILITIES</em></h1>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<h3>PENNSYLVANIA</h3>\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jrob/images/pa2.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\nLock Haven University, Lock Haven, PA\r\n\r\nJuly 5-9, 2010\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<h3>MINNESOTA</h3>\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jrob/images/mn.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\nUniversity of Minnesota, Minneapolis, MN\r\n\r\nJuly 11-15, 2010\r\n\r\n<strong>YOUTH: </strong>July 11-15, 2010\r\n\r\nJuly 18-22, 2010\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<h3>CALIFORNIA</h3>\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jrob/images/az.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\nAzusa Pacific University, Azusa, CA\r\n\r\nJuly 18-22, 2010\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<h3>WASHINGTON</h3>\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jrob/images/wa.jpg\" alt=\"image10\" /></div>\r\nCentral Washington University, Ellensburg, WA\r\n\r\nAugust 1-5, 2010\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Facilities/Housing','','publish','closed','closed','','facilitieshousing','','','2010-06-30 11:59:39','2010-06-30 16:59:39','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.n