egory=\"3\"]','','','publish','open','open','','265','','','2010-06-30 12:02:58','2010-06-30 17:02:58','',0,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/?p=265',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(266,1,'2010-06-30 10:05:38','2010-06-30 15:05:38','<div class=\"text\">\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"tertnav\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"takedown_dates.php\">Dates/Locations</a> | <a href=\"takedown_discounts.php\">Discounts/Pricing</a> | <a href=\"takedown_facilities.php\">Facilities/Housing</a> | <a href=\"takedown_travel.php\">Travel Arrangements</a> | <a href=\"takedown_insurance.php\">Insurance/Key Deposit</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>TAKEDOWN CAMP OVERVIEW</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n\r\nRun in conjunction with our Technique Camps, the Takedown Camps focus on wrestling strategies from the neutral position and instruction on \"on the feet\" maneuvers. One-on-one review sessions dissect every movement related to the neutral position.\r\n\r\nFeaturing high-profile national and regional staff, our Takedown Camps cover the neutral position. The basic fundamentals to advanced college-level match strategies are taught and reviewed with an emphasis on skill development.\r\n\r\nDaily schedules consist of three on-mat training sessions offering campers a variety of work-out partners based on age and abilityall in small group settings.\r\n\r\nEach day a different special guest will be invited to providing campers with motivational and inspirational speeches.\r\n\r\nIdeal for wrestlers 8-18 years of age.*\r\n<p class=\"small-text\">*Must be at least 10 years old to stay overnight in the dorms at Minnesota Camps.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>SAMPLE DAILY SCHEDULE</h4>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"img-holder\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/takedown-overview.jpg\" alt=\"J Robinson Intensive Wrestling Camps\" /></div>\r\n<table width=\"277\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\">7:00</td>\r\n<td width=\"230\">Wake-Up</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>9:00</td>\r\n<td>Technique Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11:00</td>\r\n<td>Free Time</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>12:00</td>\r\n<td>Lunch</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>2:00</td>\r\n<td>Technique Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>4:00</td>\r\n<td>Planned Recreation</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>5:30</td>\r\n<td>Dinner</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7:00</td>\r\n<td>Technique Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>9:45</td>\r\n<td>Motivation/Mental Attitude</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11:00</td>\r\n<td>Lights Out</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Takedown Camps','','inherit','open','open','','136-revision-4','','','2010-06-30 10:05:38','2010-06-30 15:05:38','',136,'http://aaijrob.xray.aaidev.net/archives/266',0,'revision','',0),(270,1,'2010-06-30 12:08:09','2010-06-30 17:08:09','<div class=\"text\">\r\n<h3>TRAVEL ARRANGEMENTS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jrob/images/takedown-travel.jpg\" alt=\"Travel Arrangements\" align=\"left\" />\r\nTravel arrangements to and from camp are the responsibility of each camper.\r\n\r\nCampers are to arrive the first day of camp and leave the last day of camp. Check in is from 12:00-2:00 pm on the first day of camp; check out is from 12:00-1:00 pm on the last day of camp. Travel arrangements to and from camp are the responsibility of each individual camper.\r\n\r\nJ Robinson Camps has a relationship with Teel\'s Travel for preferred airfare pricing. Contact Darcie by phone (800-233-3225), email (<a href=\"mailto:Darcie@Travel-Planners.com\">Darcie@Travel-Planners.com</a>) or online at <a href=\"http://www.travel-planners.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Travel-Planners.com</a>.\r\n\r\nRound-trip transportation to and from the airport is provided by the camps for $25 per camper. Please check your confirmation materials for the correct airport for your camp.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Travel Arrangements','','inherit','open','open','','252-revision-3','','','2010-06-30 12:08:09','2010-06-30 17:08:09','',252,'ht